{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"College presidents are not the first people who come to mind"},{"time":4000,"text":"when the subject is the uses of the creative imagination."},{"time":7000,"text":"So I thought I'd start by telling you how I got here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":11000,"text":"The story begins in the late '90s."},{"time":13000,"text":"I was invited to meet with leading educators"},{"time":16000,"text":"from the newly free Eastern Europe and Russia."},{"time":20000,"text":"They were trying to figure out how to rebuild their universities."},{"time":24000,"text":"Since education under the Soviet Union"},{"time":27000,"text":"was essentially propaganda"},{"time":29000,"text":"serving the purposes of a state ideology,"},{"time":32000,"text":"they appreciated that it would take wholesale transformations"},{"time":37000,"text":"if they were to provide an education"},{"time":39000,"text":"worthy of free men and women."},{"time":42000,"text":"Given this rare opportunity"},{"time":44000,"text":"to start fresh,"},{"time":46000,"text":"they chose liberal arts"},{"time":48000,"text":"as the most compelling model"},{"time":50000,"text":"because of its historic commitment"},{"time":52000,"text":"to furthering its students' broadest intellectual,"},{"time":55000,"text":"and deepest ethical potential."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58000,"text":"Having made that decision"},{"time":60000,"text":"they came to the United States,"},{"time":62000,"text":"home of liberal arts education,"},{"time":64000,"text":"to talk with some of us"},{"time":66000,"text":"most closely identified"},{"time":68000,"text":"with that kind of education."},{"time":70000,"text":"They spoke with a passion, an urgency,"},{"time":74000,"text":"an intellectual conviction"},{"time":76000,"text":"that, for me, was a voice I had not heard in decades,"},{"time":81000,"text":"a dream long forgotten."},{"time":83000,"text":"For, in truth, we had moved light years"},{"time":88000,"text":"from the passions that animated them."},{"time":92000,"text":"But for me, unlike them,"},{"time":96000,"text":"in my world, the slate was not clean,"},{"time":100000,"text":"and what was written on it was not encouraging."}]},{"cues":[{"time":104000,"text":"In truth, liberal arts education"},{"time":107000,"text":"no longer exists --"},{"time":109000,"text":"at least genuine liberal arts education -- in this country."},{"time":113000,"text":"We have professionalized liberal arts to the point"},{"time":116000,"text":"where they no longer provide the breadth of application"},{"time":120000,"text":"and the enhanced capacity for civic engagement"},{"time":123000,"text":"that is their signature."},{"time":125000,"text":"Over the past century"},{"time":127000,"text":"the expert has dethroned the educated generalist"},{"time":131000,"text":"to become the sole model"},{"time":134000,"text":"of intellectual accomplishment. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":136000,"text":"Expertise has for sure had its moments."},{"time":141000,"text":"But the price of its dominance is enormous."},{"time":145000,"text":"Subject matters are broken up"},{"time":147000,"text":"into smaller and smaller pieces,"},{"time":150000,"text":"with increasing emphasis on the technical and the obscure."},{"time":154000,"text":"We have even managed to make the study of literature arcane."},{"time":159000,"text":"You may think you know what is going on"},{"time":161000,"text":"in that Jane Austen novel --"},{"time":163000,"text":"that is, until your first encounter"},{"time":166000,"text":"with postmodern deconstructionism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169000,"text":"The progression of today's college student"},{"time":172000,"text":"is to jettison every interest except one."},{"time":177000,"text":"And within that one, to continually narrow the focus,"},{"time":181000,"text":"learning more and more about less and less;"},{"time":185000,"text":"this, despite the evidence all around us"},{"time":188000,"text":"of the interconnectedness of things."},{"time":191000,"text":"Lest you think I exaggerate,"},{"time":194000,"text":"here are the beginnings of the A-B-Cs of anthropology."},{"time":199000,"text":"As one moves up the ladder,"},{"time":201000,"text":"values other than technical competence"},{"time":203000,"text":"are viewed with increasing suspicion."},{"time":206000,"text":"Questions such as,"},{"time":208000,"text":"\"What kind of a world are we making?"},{"time":211000,"text":"What kind of a world should we be making?"},{"time":214000,"text":"What kind of a world can we be making?\""},{"time":217000,"text":"are treated with more and more skepticism,"},{"time":221000,"text":"and move off the table."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223000,"text":"In so doing, the guardians of secular democracy"},{"time":227000,"text":"in effect yield the connection"},{"time":231000,"text":"between education and values"},{"time":233000,"text":"to fundamentalists,"},{"time":235000,"text":"who, you can be sure,"},{"time":237000,"text":"have no compunctions about using education"},{"time":240000,"text":"to further their values:"},{"time":242000,"text":"the absolutes of a theocracy."},{"time":245000,"text":"Meanwhile, the values and voices of democracy are silent."},{"time":251000,"text":"Either we have lost touch with those values"},{"time":253000,"text":"or, no better,"},{"time":255000,"text":"believe they need not"},{"time":257000,"text":"or cannot be taught."},{"time":259000,"text":"This aversion to social values"},{"time":261000,"text":"may seem at odds with the explosion"},{"time":264000,"text":"of community service programs."},{"time":266000,"text":"But despite the attention paid to these efforts,"},{"time":269000,"text":"they remain emphatically extracurricular."},{"time":273000,"text":"In effect, civic-mindedness is treated"},{"time":276000,"text":"as outside the realm of what purports to be"},{"time":279000,"text":"serious thinking and adult purposes."},{"time":283000,"text":"Simply put, when the impulse is to change the world,"},{"time":288000,"text":"the academy is more likely to engender"},{"time":290000,"text":"a learned helplessness"},{"time":293000,"text":"than to create a sense of empowerment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297000,"text":"This brew -- oversimplification of civic engagement,"},{"time":303000,"text":"idealization of the expert,"},{"time":305000,"text":"fragmentation of knowledge,"},{"time":308000,"text":"emphasis on technical mastery,"},{"time":310000,"text":"neutrality as a condition of academic integrity --"},{"time":314000,"text":"is toxic when it comes to pursuing the vital connections"},{"time":319000,"text":"between education and the public good,"},{"time":322000,"text":"between intellectual integrity"},{"time":325000,"text":"and human freedom,"},{"time":327000,"text":"which were at the heart --"},{"time":329000,"text":"(Applause) -- of the challenge posed to and by"},{"time":333000,"text":"my European colleagues."},{"time":335000,"text":"When the astronomical distance"},{"time":337000,"text":"between the realities of the academy"},{"time":340000,"text":"and the visionary intensity of this challenge"},{"time":343000,"text":"were more than enough, I can assure you,"},{"time":345000,"text":"to give one pause,"},{"time":348000,"text":"what was happening outside higher education"},{"time":351000,"text":"made backing off unthinkable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":354000,"text":"Whether it was threats to the environment,"},{"time":357000,"text":"inequities in the distribution of wealth,"},{"time":360000,"text":"lack of a sane policy or a sustainable policy"},{"time":363000,"text":"with respect to the continuing uses of energy,"},{"time":367000,"text":"we were in desperate straits."},{"time":369000,"text":"And that was only the beginning."},{"time":372000,"text":"The corrupting of our political life"},{"time":374000,"text":"had become a living nightmare;"},{"time":376000,"text":"nothing was exempt --"},{"time":379000,"text":"separation of powers, civil liberties,"},{"time":382000,"text":"the rule of law,"},{"time":384000,"text":"the relationship of church and state."},{"time":386000,"text":"Accompanied by a squandering"},{"time":388000,"text":"of the nation's material wealth"},{"time":391000,"text":"that defied credulity."},{"time":393000,"text":"A harrowing predilection for the uses of force"},{"time":396000,"text":"had become commonplace,"},{"time":398000,"text":"with an equal distaste"},{"time":400000,"text":"for the alternative forms of influence."},{"time":403000,"text":"At the same time, all of our firepower was impotent"},{"time":408000,"text":"when it came to halting or even stemming"},{"time":411000,"text":"the slaughter in Rwanda, Darfur, Myanmar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":416000,"text":"Our public education, once a model for the world,"},{"time":420000,"text":"has become most noteworthy"},{"time":422000,"text":"for its failures."},{"time":424000,"text":"Mastery of basic skills and a bare minimum of cultural literacy"},{"time":428000,"text":"eludes vast numbers of our students."},{"time":432000,"text":"Despite having a research establishment"},{"time":434000,"text":"that is the envy of the world,"},{"time":436000,"text":"more than half of the American public"},{"time":438000,"text":"don't believe in evolution."},{"time":440000,"text":"And don't press your luck"},{"time":442000,"text":"about how much those who do believe in it"},{"time":444000,"text":"actually understand it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447000,"text":"Incredibly, this nation,"},{"time":450000,"text":"with all its material, intellectual and spiritual resources,"},{"time":456000,"text":"seems utterly helpless"},{"time":458000,"text":"to reverse the freefall in any of these areas."},{"time":463000,"text":"Equally startling, from my point of view,"},{"time":466000,"text":"is the fact that no one"},{"time":468000,"text":"was drawing any connections"},{"time":470000,"text":"between what is happening to the body politic,"},{"time":473000,"text":"and what is happening in our leading educational institutions."},{"time":477000,"text":"We may be at the top of the list"},{"time":480000,"text":"when it comes to influencing access to personal wealth."},{"time":484000,"text":"We are not even on the list"},{"time":486000,"text":"when it comes to our responsibility"},{"time":489000,"text":"for the health of this democracy."},{"time":491000,"text":"We are playing with fire."},{"time":494000,"text":"You can be sure Jefferson knew"},{"time":496000,"text":"what he was talking about when he said,"},{"time":498000,"text":"\"If a nation expects to be ignorant and free"},{"time":502000,"text":"in a state of civilization,"},{"time":504000,"text":"it expects what never was,"},{"time":506000,"text":"and never will be.\""},{"time":509000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":511000,"text":"On a more personal note,"},{"time":513000,"text":"this betrayal of our principles,"},{"time":515000,"text":"our decency, our hope,"},{"time":517000,"text":"made it impossible for me"},{"time":519000,"text":"to avoid the question,"},{"time":522000,"text":"\"What will I say, years from now,"},{"time":524000,"text":"when people ask, 'Where were you?'\""},{"time":528000,"text":"As president of a leading liberal arts college,"},{"time":530000,"text":"famous for its innovative history,"},{"time":533000,"text":"there were no excuses."},{"time":535000,"text":"So the conversation began at Bennington."},{"time":538000,"text":"Knowing that if we were to regain"},{"time":540000,"text":"the integrity of liberal education,"},{"time":542000,"text":"it would take radical rethinking"},{"time":544000,"text":"of basic assumptions,"},{"time":546000,"text":"beginning with our priorities."},{"time":549000,"text":"Enhancing the public good becomes a primary objective."},{"time":553000,"text":"The accomplishment of civic virtue"},{"time":555000,"text":"is tied to the uses of intellect and imagination"},{"time":559000,"text":"at their most challenging."}]},{"cues":[{"time":561000,"text":"Our ways of approaching agency and authority"},{"time":565000,"text":"turn inside out to reflect the reality"},{"time":569000,"text":"that no one has the answers"},{"time":572000,"text":"to the challenges facing citizens in this century,"},{"time":575000,"text":"and everyone has the responsibility"},{"time":579000,"text":"for trying and participating in finding them."},{"time":583000,"text":"Bennington would continue to teach the arts and sciences"},{"time":586000,"text":"as areas of immersion that acknowledge differences"},{"time":589000,"text":"in personal and professional objectives."},{"time":592000,"text":"But the balances redressed,"},{"time":594000,"text":"our shared purposes assume an equal"},{"time":597000,"text":"if not greater importance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":599000,"text":"When the design emerged it was surprisingly simple and straightforward."},{"time":604000,"text":"The idea is to make the political-social challenges themselves --"},{"time":608000,"text":"from health and education"},{"time":610000,"text":"to the uses of force --"},{"time":612000,"text":"the organizers of the curriculum."},{"time":615000,"text":"They would assume the commanding role of traditional disciplines."},{"time":618000,"text":"But structures designed to connect, rather than divide"},{"time":623000,"text":"mutually dependent circles,"},{"time":625000,"text":"rather than isolating triangles."},{"time":628000,"text":"And the point is not to treat these topics"},{"time":631000,"text":"as topics of study,"},{"time":633000,"text":"but as frameworks of action."},{"time":635000,"text":"The challenge: to figure out what it will take"},{"time":639000,"text":"to actually do something"},{"time":641000,"text":"that makes a significant and sustainable difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":645000,"text":"Contrary to widely held assumptions,"},{"time":648000,"text":"an emphasis on action provides a special urgency to thinking."},{"time":653000,"text":"The importance of coming to grips with values like justice,"},{"time":658000,"text":"equity, truth,"},{"time":660000,"text":"becomes increasingly evident"},{"time":662000,"text":"as students discover that interest alone"},{"time":666000,"text":"cannot tell them what they need to know"},{"time":669000,"text":"when the issue is rethinking education,"},{"time":672000,"text":"our approach to health,"},{"time":674000,"text":"or strategies for achieving"},{"time":676000,"text":"an economics of equity."},{"time":678000,"text":"The value of the past also comes alive;"},{"time":682000,"text":"it provides a lot of company."},{"time":684000,"text":"You are not the first to try to figure this out,"},{"time":687000,"text":"just as you are unlikely to be the last."},{"time":690000,"text":"Even more valuable,"},{"time":692000,"text":"history provides a laboratory"},{"time":694000,"text":"in which we see played out"},{"time":697000,"text":"the actual, as well as the intended"},{"time":700000,"text":"consequences of ideas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":703000,"text":"In the language of my students,"},{"time":705000,"text":"\"Deep thought matters"},{"time":707000,"text":"when you're contemplating what to do"},{"time":709000,"text":"about things that matter.\""},{"time":712000,"text":"A new liberal arts that can support this"},{"time":714000,"text":"action-oriented curriculum"},{"time":716000,"text":"has begun to emerge."},{"time":718000,"text":"Rhetoric, the art of organizing the world of words"},{"time":722000,"text":"to maximum effect."},{"time":724000,"text":"Design, the art of organizing the world of things."},{"time":729000,"text":"Mediation and improvisation"},{"time":731000,"text":"also assume a special place in this new pantheon."},{"time":736000,"text":"Quantitative reasoning attains its proper position"},{"time":739000,"text":"at the heart of what it takes to manage change"},{"time":743000,"text":"where measurement is crucial."},{"time":745000,"text":"As is a capacity to discriminate"},{"time":748000,"text":"systematically between what is at the core"},{"time":751000,"text":"and what is at the periphery."}]},{"cues":[{"time":753000,"text":"And when making connections is of the essence,"},{"time":756000,"text":"the power of technology emerges with special intensity."},{"time":761000,"text":"But so does the importance of content."},{"time":764000,"text":"The more powerful our reach,"},{"time":766000,"text":"the more important the question \"About what?\""},{"time":770000,"text":"When improvisation, resourcefulness, imagination are key,"},{"time":774000,"text":"artists, at long last,"},{"time":777000,"text":"take their place at the table,"},{"time":779000,"text":"when strategies of action are in the process of being designed."},{"time":785000,"text":"In this dramatically expanded ideal"},{"time":787000,"text":"of a liberal arts education"},{"time":789000,"text":"where the continuum of thought and action is its life's blood,"},{"time":793000,"text":"knowledge honed outside the academy"},{"time":796000,"text":"becomes essential."},{"time":798000,"text":"Social activists, business leaders,"},{"time":801000,"text":"lawyers, politicians, professionals"},{"time":803000,"text":"will join the faculty as active and ongoing participants"},{"time":808000,"text":"in this wedding of liberal education to the advancement of the public good."},{"time":812000,"text":"Students, in turn, continuously move outside the classroom"},{"time":817000,"text":"to engage the world directly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":820000,"text":"And of course, this new wine"},{"time":823000,"text":"needs new bottles"},{"time":825000,"text":"if we are to capture the liveliness and dynamism"},{"time":829000,"text":"of this idea."},{"time":831000,"text":"The most important discovery we made"},{"time":833000,"text":"in our focus on public action"},{"time":836000,"text":"was to appreciate that the hard choices"},{"time":839000,"text":"are not between good and evil,"},{"time":842000,"text":"but between competing goods."},{"time":845000,"text":"This discovery is transforming."},{"time":848000,"text":"It undercuts self-righteousness,"},{"time":850000,"text":"radically alters the tone and character of controversy,"},{"time":854000,"text":"and enriches dramatically"},{"time":856000,"text":"the possibilities for finding common ground."},{"time":859000,"text":"Ideology, zealotry,"},{"time":861000,"text":"unsubstantiated opinions simply won't do."},{"time":866000,"text":"This is a political education, to be sure."},{"time":870000,"text":"But it is a politics of principle,"},{"time":873000,"text":"not of partisanship."},{"time":875000,"text":"So the challenge for Bennington is to do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":878000,"text":"On the cover of Bennington's 2008 holiday card"},{"time":882000,"text":"is the architect's sketch of a building"},{"time":884000,"text":"opening in 2010"},{"time":886000,"text":"that is to be a center for the advancement"},{"time":888000,"text":"of public action."},{"time":890000,"text":"The center will embody and sustain this new educational commitment."},{"time":895000,"text":"Think of it as a kind of secular church."},{"time":898000,"text":"The words on the card describe what will happen inside."},{"time":902000,"text":"We intend to turn the intellectual"},{"time":904000,"text":"and imaginative power, passion and boldness"},{"time":907000,"text":"of our students, faculty and staff"},{"time":911000,"text":"to developing strategies"},{"time":913000,"text":"for acting on the critical challenges of our time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":917000,"text":"So we are doing our job."},{"time":920000,"text":"While these past weeks have been a time"},{"time":922000,"text":"of national exhilaration in this country,"},{"time":925000,"text":"it would be tragic if you thought this meant"},{"time":928000,"text":"your job was done."},{"time":930000,"text":"The glacial silence we have experienced"},{"time":933000,"text":"in the face of the shredding of the constitution,"},{"time":936000,"text":"the unraveling of our public institutions,"},{"time":939000,"text":"the deterioration of our infrastructure"},{"time":941000,"text":"is not limited to the universities."},{"time":943000,"text":"We the people"},{"time":945000,"text":"have become inured to our own irrelevance"},{"time":949000,"text":"when it comes to doing anything significant"},{"time":951000,"text":"about anything that matters"},{"time":953000,"text":"concerning governance,"},{"time":955000,"text":"beyond waiting another four years."},{"time":958000,"text":"We persist also"},{"time":961000,"text":"in being sidelined by the idea of the expert"},{"time":964000,"text":"as the only one capable of coming up with answers,"},{"time":967000,"text":"despite the overwhelming evidence to the contrary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":972000,"text":"The problem is there is no such thing"},{"time":977000,"text":"as a viable democracy made up of experts,"},{"time":981000,"text":"zealots, politicians and spectators."},{"time":985000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":992000,"text":"People will continue and should continue"},{"time":994000,"text":"to learn everything there is to know about something or other."},{"time":997000,"text":"We actually do it all the time."},{"time":1000000,"text":"And there will be and should be"},{"time":1002000,"text":"those who spend a lifetime"},{"time":1004000,"text":"pursuing a very highly defined area of inquiry."},{"time":1008000,"text":"But this single-mindedness will not yield"},{"time":1011000,"text":"the flexibilities of mind,"},{"time":1013000,"text":"the multiplicity of perspectives,"},{"time":1016000,"text":"the capacities for collaboration and innovation"},{"time":1019000,"text":"this country needs."},{"time":1021000,"text":"That is where you come in."},{"time":1023000,"text":"What is certain is that the individual talent"},{"time":1027000,"text":"exhibited in such abundance here,"},{"time":1030000,"text":"needs to turn its attention"},{"time":1033000,"text":"to that collaborative, messy, frustrating,"},{"time":1037000,"text":"contentious and impossible world"},{"time":1040000,"text":"of politics and public policy."},{"time":1042000,"text":"President Obama and his team"},{"time":1045000,"text":"simply cannot do it alone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1048000,"text":"If the question of where to start seems overwhelming"},{"time":1052000,"text":"you are at the beginning, not the end of this adventure."},{"time":1055000,"text":"Being overwhelmed is the first step"},{"time":1058000,"text":"if you are serious about trying to get at things that really matter,"},{"time":1062000,"text":"on a scale that makes a difference."},{"time":1065000,"text":"So what do you do when you feel overwhelmed?"},{"time":1068000,"text":"Well, you have two things."},{"time":1071000,"text":"You have a mind. And you have other people."},{"time":1074000,"text":"Start with those, and change the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1079000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}